<h1 id="graphics">Graphics</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://blender.org">Blender</a> - 3D modeling, animation, and video editor</li>
  <li><a href="http://gimp.org">Gimp</a> - Photo manipulation</li>
  <li><a href="http://krita.org">Krita</a> - Photo manipulation and digital painting</li>
  <li><a href="http://mypaint.org">MyPaint</a> - Digital painting</li>
  <li><a href="http://inkscape.org">Inkscape</a> - Vector graphics editor</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="audio">Audio</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://ardour.org">Ardour</a> - Digital Audio Workstation (The official binary costs money, but you can compile it yourself or get it from somewhere else)</li>
  <li><a href="http://audacityteam.org">Audacity</a> - Audio Editor</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="utilities">Utilities</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://ffmpeg.org">FFmpeg</a> - A command line based, cross-platform solution to record, convert and stream audio and video.</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="office">Office</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://libreoffice.org">Libreoffice</a> - Office suite</li>
  <li><a href="http://abisource.com">Abiword</a> - Simple word processor</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="code">Code</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://vim.org">Vim</a> - Advanced modal text editor</li>
  <li><a href="http://git-scm.com">Git</a> - Version Control System</li>
  <li><a href="http://latex-project.org">LaTeX</a> - High Quality Typesetting System</li>
  <li><a href="http://lilypond.org">Lilypond</a> - Music Typesetting Markup</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="android-apps">Android Apps</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://f-droid.org">F-Droid</a> - App store for open source apps</li>
  <li><a href="http://newpipe.schabi.org">Newpipe</a> - Alternative Youtube browser. Downloading, external players, and no ads. (F-Droid)</li>
  <li><a href="http://andbible.github.io">Andbible</a> - Offline Bible App (F-droid or Google Play)</li>
  <li><a href="http://github.com/PaulWoitaschek/Voice">Voice</a> - Minimalistic Audio Book Player (F-droid or Google Play)</li>
</ul>

<h1 id="operating-systems">Operating Systems</h1>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://archlinux.org">Arch Linux</a> - My main OS.</li>
  <li><a href="http://voidlinux.org">Void Linux</a> - Fun minimalistic OS.</li>
</ul>
